Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.63,SCR,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz354.5\fs75\shad0\bord0\fn方正卡通_GBK\an8\c&H360D2F&\pos(1402,522)}东京超级之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.63,SCR,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fs45\fn方正FW童趣POP体 简\an8\c&H360D2F&\frz353.4\pos(1436,864)}松下先生专属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.34,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,千束 传电子版给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.98,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:16.98,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就交给他们就好 你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:26.37,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在靠着机器才能生活 很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:31.62,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有呢 我也是哦 这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.08,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,起搏器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.71,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦 一整个都是机器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.17,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,是人工心脏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.59,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,你心脏是被狗啃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.84,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,狗才不会啃机器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.22,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.43,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:52.38,TextCHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\shad0\bord0.1\blur9\an8\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(950,70)}阅读文档模式
